<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-image-container">
    <img src="<%= asset_path('lambo.jpg') %>" alt="Hero" class="hero-image">
  </div>
  <p class="hero-caption">
    Content creation for brands
    <a href="/contact" class="hero-button">CONTACT</a>
  </p>
</section>

<section class="intro">
  <img src="<%= asset_path('martin.jpg') %>" alt="Martin Nikolaev" class="intro-image">
  <div class="intro-details">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>I make high-quality videos and photos that help brands stand out — especially when it comes to cars. There’s something about capturing a fast car in the right light that I never get tired of. I’ve worked with luxury dealerships, rental services, and individual collectors to bring their vehicles to life on screen. Alongside that, I also shoot weddings and commercial spaces with the same attention to detail. Whatever the subject, I focus on clean, polished visuals that reflect the style and quality of each client.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="subjects">
  <h2>What I Photograph</h2>
  <div class="subjects-grid">
    <% ["Luxury Cars", "Restaurants", "Real State"].each do |item| %>
      <div class="subject-card">
        <img src="<%= asset_path('not-found.jpg') %>" alt="<%= item %>" class="subject-image">
        <h3><%= item %></h3>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="social-section">
  <p>Follow me for more:</p>
  <div class="social-links">
    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/martin_nikolaev/">Instagram</a>
    <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@martin_nikolaev">TikTok</a>
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@martin.nikolaev">YouTube</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-section">
  <h2>About My Work</h2>
  <p>I capture high-end visuals with a focus on automotive elegance. Whether it’s a Ferrari, a bridal moment, or a boutique hotel — every frame is composed with care.</p>
  <details class="faq">
    <summary>Do you work internationally?</summary>
    <p>Yes, I travel worldwide for select projects.</p>
  </details>
</section>

